title: The Family Handyman - July & August 2010 (Malestrom)
description:
The Family Handyman - July/August 2010
English | 92 pages | PDF

Family Handyman Magazine: Why pay for pricey repairs when you can save money and time doing it all yourself? Edited for the DIY type, Family Handyman is your guide to home, automobile and appliance repair. Featuring step-by-step instructions and clear photos, this magazine is as vital of a tool as the ones at your workbench.
